The paper deals with optimization of resource management in heterogeneous networks, which involves designing the transceivers and determining the active set of base stations. This is a problem that is commonly studied in the fields of information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), systems and control (cs.SY), multimedia (cs.MM), and machine learning (cs.LG). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories that this paper belongs to, ordered from most to least likely.
